{"tid":2394622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加拿大指香港拒絕領事館為雙重國籍被拘人士提供協助","createTime":"2021-02-04T09:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T02:43:49.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5dcb7a388da5ab227d2093e0c168e5e34d36e6b5","tid":2394622,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T09:56:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574095-20210204.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574095-20210204.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRLccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=e5e2a06a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574095-20210204.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e75a65da\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574095-20210204.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n加拿大外交部表示，香港拒絕外國領事館接觸被拘留的雙重國籍人士，以提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述五名外交官說，香港政府自回歸以來，大致上容許雙重國籍人士與領事館接觸，但情況自去年港區國安法實施後開始改變。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大上月18日接到通知，一名擁有加拿大和中國國籍的香港囚犯，被告知需要就國籍作出宣稱，又指有跡象顯示，越來越多在港被囚、擁有雙重國籍的人士，遇到同樣情況。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大外交部發言人說，希望獲得他們領事服務的加籍人士，任何時間都應該展示加籍身份。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述香港保安局發言人說，除非一名香港居民向入境處申請更改國籍，否則他仍然是中國公民。"},{"pid":"289d6ceab4325ea2f00507b654d06e6083baeedc","tid":2394622,"uid":227217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T09:59:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bfdd37e573b9695920f659c281fbdcd7a5ca6b95","tid":2394622,"uid":39872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T09:59:38.000Z","msg":"中你老母公民<br />\n違反中英聯合聲明<br />\n國籍已可重置一次<br />\n首先我唔係中國公民<br />\n你可以連我啲mpf一齊走"},{"pid":"dddbab32e5c5c05abefaa32326671d91d34d18c6","tid":2394622,"uid":123774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:02:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老母冇人想做支那狗<br />\n咪撚夾硬安個國籍俾人"},{"pid":"e148a4c32be23340d122253e16db4eb3b0d1b865","tid":2394622,"uid":271894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:03:27.000Z","msg":"全地球都係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"798121cd6a17fea4b431870e140354d2bed8ef57","tid":2394622,"uid":366932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:04:24.000Z","msg":"撤僑啦<br />\n之前已經準備好唔承認雙重國籍就撤僑"},{"pid":"19716cd4b02781a3f0f791143127308a1db1d74b","tid":2394622,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:04:49.000Z","msg":"咁即係話香港呢邊講大話姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6d6afc79c9861a85c490644e557887e1807dbe","tid":2394622,"uid":27411,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:06:14.000Z","msg":"又嚟首先係中國人，上次瑞典單野已經搞慶班鬼佬，唔知仲以為而家係清帝國年代"},{"pid":"d4e80cb5e7644c8e5c39c8b39ae0fd7cb21e000d","tid":2394622,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:06:51.000Z","msg":"香港政府犯國際法<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b128ca75548bbeb97e87c6d16e0eb0906d44d86","tid":2394622,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:06:55.000Z","msg":"加拿大幾時郁溫哥華班賤種中國人,香港藍絲<br />\n捉100個退休香港高官咪得"},{"pid":"fc20dd10b650864e96aa2f8d846722ae9342001e","tid":2394622,"uid":292544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:09:50.000Z","msg":"圖蝦多夠咩膽出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5fb41ca13a80632844b0030ae0c67a43f0947b","tid":2394622,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b128ca75548bbeb97e87c6d16e0eb0906d44d86","tid":2394622,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:06:55.000Z","msg":"加拿大幾時郁溫哥華班賤種中國人,香港藍絲<br />\n捉100個退休香港高官咪得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:11:10.000Z","msg":"爛仔鬥紳士 爛仔擺到明知你唔會除低套西裝同佢揪"},{"pid":"014cc62b17adc5e689dd1c72e72e1fa13db7b827","tid":2394622,"uid":320902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:12:35.000Z","msg":"推上國際"},{"pid":"68c89e4e4b8b5a9b5de28e6572221ed9c18a4c1b","tid":2394622,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:12:39.000Z","msg":"報道引述香港保安局發言人說，除非一名香港居民向入境處申請更改國籍，否則他仍然是中國公民。<br />\n<br />\n同桂民海一樣"},{"pid":"6d5c2811d115972d74af98ed848161c8c7614594","tid":2394622,"uid":380027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:16:24.000Z","msg":"囚犯之後就到其他市民，中共定外國藉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e624f2b12ea3c90e93fd2e037a69ce05efb44f","tid":2394622,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:43:49.000Z","msg":"都係個句 直接制裁香港政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同撤僑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}